window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This superlative collection of futuristic tales explores ground-breaking supernatural themes from the founding heroes of the science-fiction genre. The short story form is perfect for capturing the atmospheric tension of these legendary stories. The collection includes: \"The Door in the Wall\" by H. G. Wells, \"All Cats Are Gray\" by Andre Norton, \"A Martian Odyssey\" by Stanley G. Weinbaum, \"Victory\" by Lester del Rey, \"The Moon Is Green\" by Fritz Leiber, \"The Winds of Time\" by James H. Schmitz, \"The Defenders\" by Philip K. Dick, and \"Missing Link\" by Frank Herbert.</p>"; 
